Unity 2019.1.3f1
Extra Credit Game Jam #4 - June 2019
2d racing Platformer

time based - countdown
minimap
you design platforms for your character to race through the level as fast as you can to reach point A to point B.
level can be premade or empty

need items to generate with rigidbody and/or box colliders
need start, finish, and timer countdown locations
need jump, climb, run mechanic
need ui control for blocks, slow down time (hard mode - no time stop)

sound for walk, run, jump, place, bgm, game over, click, hover

art for level, exit, player